Brain Health Registry BASELINE QUESTIONNAIRE

Source: R/data.R
BHR_BASELINE_QUESTIONNAIRE.Rd

Brain Health Registry BASELINE QUESTIONNAIRE data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(BHR_BASELINE_QUESTIONNAIRE)

Format

A data frame with 95 observations and 73 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI1

  • RID character Participant roster ID

  • PTID character Subject code obtained from the CogState Brief Battery CRF report

  • Timepoint character , with options: m00

  • CollectedDateTime POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD

  • CollectedDate_DRVD Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • Latest numeric Range value: 1, ..., 1

  • QID49 numeric How often do you use a computer? 1=Daily;2=Weekly;3=Monthly;4=Almost never

  • QID50 numeric How confident are you with computers? 1=Not confident at all;2=I usually need help;3=It depends on the task;4=Confident

  • QID4 numeric Have your children, your sibling(s), or parent(s) ever been diagnosed with Alzheimer's Disease? 1=Yes;2=No

  • QID2 numeric Are you concerned that you have a memory problem? 1=Yes;2=No

  • QID3 numeric Do you have trouble remembering if you have already told someone something? 1=Yes;2=No

  • QID5 numeric Compared to 10 years ago, would you say there has been a change in your memory? 1=Yes;2=No

  • QID20 numeric In general, would you say your health is: 1=Excellent;2=Very Good;3=Good;4=Fair;5=Poor

  • QID7 numeric Compared to one year ago, how would you rate your health in general now? 1=Much Better;2=Better;3=Same;4=Worse;5=Much Worse

  • QID8 numeric Are you in good spirits most of the time? 1=Yes;2=No

  • QID21 numeric Have you dropped many of your activities and interests? 1=Yes;2=No

  • QID38 numeric Stress means a situation in which a person feels tense, restless, nervous or anxious or is unable to sleep at night because his/her mind is troubled all the time. During the past 12 months, would you say you experienced: 1=A lot of stress;2=A moderate amount of stress;3=Relatively little stress;4=Almost no stress at all

  • QID22 numeric Please indicate whether you currently have or had experienced alcohol abuse in the past. 1=Yes;3=No

  • QID23_TEXT numeric How long has it been in years since you stopped your alcohol abuse? If you still abuse alcohol please write 0. Range value: 10, ..., 11

  • QID41 numeric Please indicate whether you currently have or had experienced drug abuse in the past. 1=Yes;2=No

  • QID42_TEXT logical How long has it been in years since you stopped the drug abuse? If you still abuse drugs please write 0. Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • QID15_1 numeric Are you currently taking any of the following types of medications? (Select all that apply)... Anti-depressant medication 1=Yes;=No

  • QID15_2 numeric Are you currently taking any of the following types of medications? (Select all that apply)... Anti-anxiety medication 1=Yes;=No
